l','You can select from a list of commonly generated formats.<br /><b>Original:</b><br /><i>Categories:</i> category-name-c-34<br /><i>Products:</i> product-name-p-54<br /><br /><b>Category Parent:</b><br /><i>Categories:</i> parent-category-name-c-34<br /><i>Products:</i> parent-product-name-p-54',33,4,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_url_format_option','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'enable-original\\\', \\\'enable-parent\\\'),'),(658,'Categories as directories','SEO_URL_CATEGORY_DIR','short','You can select from a list of commonly generated formats.<br /><b>Off:</b> disables displaying categories as directories<br /><br /><b>Short:</b> use the settings from \'Format of rewritten URLs\'<b>Full:</b> uses full category paths<br /><br />',33,5,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_category_dir_option','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'disable\\\', \\\'enable-short\\\', \\\'enable-full\\\'),'),(659,'Enter PCRE filter rules for generated URLs','SEO_URLS_FILTER_PCRE','','This setting uses PCRE rules to filter generated urls.<br><br>The format <b>MUST</b> be in the form: <b>find1=>replace1,find2=>replace2</b>. This filter is run before character conversions and stripping of special characters. If you want a dash - in your URLS, use a single space. Also note you must double escape back slashes.',33,6,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','',''),(660,'Enter special character conversions','SEO_URLS_FILTER_CHARS','','This setting will replace a single byte character with another single byte character.<br><br>The format <b>MUST</b> be in the form: <b>char=>conv,char2=>conv2</b>',33,7,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','',''),(661,'Remove these characters from URLs','SEO_URLS_REMOVE_CHARS','punctuation','This allows you remove certain problematic characters from the generated URLs.<br /><br /><i>non-alphanumerical:</i> removes all non-alphanumerical characters<br /><i>punctuation:</i> removes all punctuation characters',33,8,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_remove_chars_option','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'enable-non-alphanumerical\\\', \\\'enable-punctuation\\\'),'),(662,'Filter Short Words','SEO_URLS_FILTER_SHORT_WORDS','0','This setting will filter words less than or equal to the value from the URL.',33,9,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','',''),(663,'Enter pages to allow rewrite','SEO_URLS_ONLY_IN','index, product_info, product_music_info, document_general_info, document_product_info, product_free_shipping_info, products_new, products_all, shopping_cart, featured_products, specials, contact_us, conditions, privacy, reviews, shippinginfo, faqs_all, site_map, gv_faq, discount_coupon, page, page_2, page_3, page_4','You can limit the pages which will be rewritten by specifying them here. If no pages are specified all pages will be rewritten. <br><br>The format is comma delimited and <b>MUST</b> be in the form: <b>page1,page2,page3</b> or <b>page1, page2, page3</b>',33,10,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','',''),(664,'Choose URL Rewrite Engine','SEO_REWRITE_TYPE','rewrite','Choose which URL Rewrite Engine to use.',33,11,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'rewrite\\\'),'),(665,'Enable automatic redirects?','SEO_USE_REDIRECT','false','This will activate the automatic redirect code and send 301 headers for old to new URLs.',33,12,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'true\\\', \\\'false\\\'),'),(666,'Enable SEO cache to save queries?','SEO_USE_CACHE_GLOBAL','true','This is a global setting and will turn off caching completely.',33,13,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_cache_options','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'enable\\\', \\\'disable\\\'),'),(667,'Enable product cache?','SEO_USE_CACHE_PRODUCTS','true','This will turn off caching for the products.',33,14,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_cache_options','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'enable-products\\\', \\\'disable-products\\\'),'),(668,'Enable categories cache?','SEO_USE_CACHE_CATEGORIES','true','This will turn off caching for the categories.',33,15,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_cache_options','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'enable-categories\\\', \\\'disable-categories\\\'),'),(669,'Enable manufacturers cache?','SEO_USE_CACHE_MANUFACTURERS','true','This will turn off caching for the manufacturers.',33,16,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_cache_options','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'enable-manufacturers\\\', \\\'disable-manufacturers\\\'),'),(670,'Enable ez pages cache?','SEO_USE_CACHE_EZ_PAGES','true','This will turn off caching for ez pages.',33,17,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_check_cache_options','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'enable-ez_pages\\\', \\\'disable-ez_pages\\\'),'),(671,'Reset SEO URLs Cache','SEO_URLS_CACHE_RESET','false','This will reset the cache data for SEO',33,18,'2015-08-03 22:53:05','2015-08-03 22:52:00','usu_reset_cache_data','zen_cfg_select_option(array(\\\'true\\\', \\\'false\\\'),'),(672,'COWOA','COWOA_STATUS','true','Activate COWOA Checkout? <br />Set to True to allow a customer to checkout without an account.',34,10,'2015-08-05 21:23:22','2015-08-05 21:16:34',NULL,'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'true\', \'false\'),'),(673,'Turn Off Sideboxes During Checkout','COWOA_SIDEBOX_OFF','false','Turn off sideboxes during checkout? <br /><br />Customers should be focused on completing the sale once they start the checkout process. It is a recommended practice that sideboxes should be turned off to help minimize customer distractions during checkout. Many of the larger e-commerce retailers turn off \"distractions\" during their checkout processes for the same reason - i.e. Amazon. By reducing customer distractions during checkout you can help to decrease cart abandonment, and to increase sales conversions.<br /><br />Set to True to turn off the following sideboxes during checkout:<br /><ul><li>account_history_info (Order Information)</li><li>account_newsletters (Newsletter Subscriptions)</li><li>account_notifications (Product Notifications)</li><li>account_password (My Password)</li><li>address_book (My Personal Address Book)</li><li>address_book_process (New Address Book Entry)</li><li>checkout_confirmation (Confirmation/Order Review)</li><li>checkout_payment (Payment Method/Payment Information)</li><li>checkout_payment_address (Change Billing Address/Change the Billing Information)</li><li>checkout_process (submits the order)</li><li>checkout_shipping (Shipping Method/Shipping Information)</li><li>checkout_shipping_address (Change Shipping Address/Change the Shipping Address)</li><li>create_account (Create Account/My Account Information)</li><li>login (Login)</li><li>logoff Logoff)</li><li>no_account (COWOA Billing Information)</li><li>shopping_cart (Shopping Cart)</li></ul>',34,12,NULL,'2015-08-05 21:16:34',NULL,'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'true\', \'false\'),'),(674,'Enable Order Status','COWOA_ORDER_STATUS','true','Enable The Order Status Function of COWOA?<br />Set to True so that a Customer that uses COWOA will receive an E-Mail with instructions on how to view the status of their order.',34,14,'2015-08-05 21:24:41','2015-08-05 21:16:34',NULL,'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'true\', \'false\'),'),(675,'Enable E-Mail Only','COWOA_EMAIL_ONLY','true','Enable The E-Mail Order Function of COWOA?<br />Set to True so that a Customer that uses COWOA will only need to enter their E-Mail Address upon checkout if their Cart Balance is 0 (Free).',34,16,'2015-08-05 21:24:46','2015-08-05 21:16:34',NULL,'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'true\', \'false\'),'),(676,'Enable Forced Logoff','COWOA_LOGOFF','true','Enable The Forced LogOff Function of COWOA?<br />Set to True so that a Customer that uses COWOA will be logged off automatically after a sucessfull checkout. If they are getting a file download, then they will have to wait for the Status E-Mail to arrive in order to download the file.',34,18,'2015-08-05 21:24:50','2015-08-05 21:16:34',NULL,'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'true\', \'false\'),'),(677,'Include a link to the Font Awesome stylesheet?','CSS3_BUTTONS_INCLUDE_FONT_AWESOME','false','If true, a link to the Font Awesome CSS file will be included in each page\'s header.  If your template already includes Font Awesome, leave this setting <em>false</em>.',19,148,NULL,'0001-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'true\', \'false\'),'),(678,'Font Awesome version number','CSS3_BUTTONS_FONT_AWESOME_VERSION','4.2.0','Enter the Font Awesome version number to load, if the previous setting is set to <em>true</em>. Default: 4.2.0',19,150,NULL,'0001-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL),(679,'Submit-button HTML Tag','CSS3_BUTTONS_SUBMIT_TYPE','input','Identify the type of HTML tag to use for CSS-generated submit buttons, either <em>input</em> (default) or <em>button</em>.  Please note that the <em>button</em> tag is not fully supported on older browsers.',19,152,NULL,'0001-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,'zen_cfg_select_option(array(\'button\', \'input\'),'),(964,'JQuery CDNæ‰˜ç®¡æºé€‰æ‹©','GPE_JQUERY_LIBRARY_CDN_SOURCE','Google','<br class=\"clearBoth\" />è¯·åœ¨ä¸‹é¢é€‰æ‹©JQuery CDN æ‰˜ç®¡æº,<br class=\"clearBoth\" />åº”ç”¨æœ¬é¡¹éœ€è¦å…ˆå¯ç”¨ JQueryåº“CDNæ‰˜ç®¡åŠ é€Ÿ é¡¹,<br class=\"clearBoth\" />é»˜è®¤ Google ;<br class=\"clearBoth\" /><p style=\"padding-left: 10px;\"><span style=\"width:70px; display: block; float: left;\">æ¨¡å—åˆ¶ä½œ:</span> <span style=\"display: block; float: left;\">By KIRA</span><br class=\"clearBoth\" /><span style=\"width:70px; display: block; float: left;\">QQ: </span><span style=\"display: block; float: left;\">6171718</span><br class=\"clearBoth\" /><span style=\"width:70px; display: block; float: left;\">email: </span><a href=\"mailto:kira@kpa7.net\" title=\"ç»™KIRAå‘é‚®ä»¶\" /><span style=\"display: block; float: left;\">kira@kpa7.net</span></a><br cla